Class SubtenantUserListOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing.FilterOptions
      • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing.ListOptions
        • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.accounts.model.SubtenantUserListOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    @Preamble(description="Options to use when listing subtenant users.")
public class SubtenantUserListOptions
extends ListOptions
    Options to use when listing subtenant users.

    Note:

    • Filters:

      The list can be filtered server-side on some of the fields of a subtenant user.

      The following filters are currently supported:

      Server-side filters
      Field Tag Filters
      not equal to equal to greater than less than like in not in
      loginProfiles TAG_FILTER_BY_LOGIN_PROFILES •
      status TAG_FILTER_BY_STATUS • • •
      email TAG_FILTER_BY_EMAIL •
